name: Tour Etihad's FIRST CLASS Lounge in Abu Dhabi!
description:
Let's check out Etihad's over-the-top First Class Lounge in Abu Dhabi. It's fantastic! This video tour explores nearly every corner of this over-the-top lounge. From the meal service, to the bar, and the endless seating options, this is my favorite lounge on the planet. What do you think?

Be sure to subscribe:
